					</li>
					<li>
						Knird will continually learn each customer's individual taste preferences and leverage those learnings to 
						better serve each customer. 
					</li>
					<li>
						Knird will create both technology and a business model to ensure customers get personalized 
						service without paying a premium. 
					</li>
				</ul>  
			</h4>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
